'''德妮兹·加姆澤·埃爾居文'''（{{lang-tr|Deniz Gamze Ergüven}}，{{IPA-tr|dɛniz gamzɛ ɛɾgy'vɛn|pron}}，{{bd|1978年|6月4日}}）是一位[[土耳其|土耳其]]裔[[法國|法國]]女導演、編劇及演員，其2015年導演處女作《[[少女離家日記|少女離家日記]]》獲[[奧斯卡最佳外語片|奧斯卡最佳外語片]]提名。

==早年經歷==
埃爾居文於1978年6月4日出生於土耳其首都[[安卡拉|安卡拉]]，1980年代移居法國並接受教育，并於2008年從法國國立高等職業影音學院{{link-en|費米斯|La Fémis}}畢業。<ref>{{cite web |last=Riousse |first=Louise |title=4 QUESTIONS À DENIZ GAMZE ERGÜVEN, RÉALISATRICE DE MUSTANG |url=http://cheekmagazine.fr/culture/4-questions-deniz-gamze-erguven-realisatrice-mustang/ |date=2015-06-17 |access-date=2019-18-14 |language=fr |archive-date=2015-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124164832/http://cheekmagazine.fr/culture/4-questions-deniz-gamze-erguven-realisatrice-mustang/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==職業經歷==
埃爾居文導演處女作《少女離家日記》入選[[2015年戛納電影節|2015年戛納電影節]][[導演雙周|導演雙周]]單元，獲得歐羅巴電影院綫品牌獎（{{lang|en|Europa Cinemas Label}}），<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.quinzaine-realisateurs.com/the-directors-fortnight-2015-selection-p487.html |title=The Directors' Fortnight 2015 selection! |publisher=[[導演雙週|導演雙週]] |access-date=2015-04-21 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423224901/http://www.quinzaine-realisateurs.com/the-directors-fortnight-2015-selection-p487.html |archive-date=2015-04-23 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Chang |first=Justin |url=https://variety.com/2015/film/festivals/cannes-directors-fortnight-lineup-unveiled-1201476479/ |title=Cannes: Directors' Fortnight Unveils 2015 Lineup |publisher=[[綜藝_(雜志)|綜藝]] |date=2015-04-21 |access-date=2015-04-21 |language=en |archive-date=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815000511/https://variety.com/2015/film/festivals/cannes-directors-fortnight-lineup-unveiled-1201476479/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Ford |first=Rebecca |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-2015-directors-fortnight-awards-797335 |title=Cannes: 'Embrace of the Serpent' Tops Directors' Fortnight Awards |publisher=[[好萊塢報道|好萊塢報道]] |date=2015-05-22 |access-date=2019-08-14 |language=en |archive-date=2019-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615123210/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-2015-directors-fortnight-awards-797335 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=Quinzaine |author=導演雙週 |author-link=導演雙週 |number=601807295052435456 |date=2015-05-22 |title=Mention to "The Exquisite Corpus de/by Peter Tscherkassky #quinzaine2015 |access-date=2019-08-14 |language=en}}</ref>並代表法國角逐[[第88届奧斯卡金像獎|第88届奧斯卡金像獎]]最佳外語片，<ref name="France">{{cite web |last=Richford |first=Rhonda |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mustang-is-frances-oscars-2015-822899 |title=Oscars: France Selects 'Mustang' As Foreign-Language Submission |publisher=好萊塢報道 |date=2015-09-22 |access-date=2019-08-14 |language=en |archive-date=2019-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814205322/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mustang-is-frances-oscars-2015-822899 |dead-url=no }}</ref>同時亦獲[[金球獎最佳外語片|金球獎最佳外語片]]提名。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Merry |first1=Stephanie |last2=Yahr |first2=Emily |title=Golden Globes nominations 2016: Complete list and analysis; Schumer, Stallone nominated; 'Carol' leads with five |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2015/12/10/golden-globes-nominations-2016-complete-coverage/ |publisher=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] |date=2015-12-10 |access-date=2019-08-14 |language=en |archive-date=2015-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210203643/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2015/12/10/golden-globes-nominations-2016-complete-coverage/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年5月，埃爾居文宣佈其下一部電影《{{link-en|洛杉磯大劫難|Kings (2017 film)|-{zh-cn:洛杉矶大劫难; zh-hk:洛杉磯黑夜; zh-tw:暴動之城;}-}}》。影片於2017年9月13日在[[2017年多倫多國際影展|多倫多國際影展]]舉行全球首映，反響欠佳。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kings_2017/ |title=Kings (2017) |website=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]] |access-date=2019-08-14 |language=en |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924170947/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kings_2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

